 9. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1
10. the person playing bridge is between the person playing go and the person eating strawberry##2
11. the person playing chess is the person eating pineapple##1
12. the person playing canasta is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1
13. the person playing canasta is between the person eating strawberry and the person playing scrabble##2
